data.description: This charming single-family home located at 1617 Jewel St in Pineville, LA was built in 1958 and boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, a spacious finished area of 1,997 sq.ft., and sits on a large lot size of 0.52 acres. With its vintage charm and ample space.Located on a quiet dead end street, with a double city lot, we've loved calling this our home for the past 13 years. During that time here are some of the updates that have been completed:-HVAC system with 2 years parts and labor warranty still remaining-New attic insulation -All three bathrooms have been remodeled -Water heater replaced 5 years ago-New stove/oven, microwave, & dishwasher -Architectural shingle roof (with lifetime manufacturer's warranty) replaced November 2023
